Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Version: @PACKAGE_VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: GlassToKey
Depends: libevdev2, udev
Description: GlassToKey Linux runtime and device picker
 GlassToKey turns Apple Magic Trackpads into keyboard input on Linux.
 This package installs the Linux runtime, udev permissions, user service unit,
 and optional GUI launcher when the GUI publish output is included.
